job_name = "CHAR_MARVELOUS_TRAVELER"
description = "Dai Zong, the Marvelous Traveler. In the legend he marched five hundred li in a day by a charm tied to his legs, the brotherhood's courier and eyes. Here a transit-runner whose gift outruns the trains, first to know everything and last to sit still. Wry, restless, always already gone."
